_:Nfabe38f071b14227af3d5434b05f723a <http://schema.org/name> "John Vickerman" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/john-vickerman> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "John Vickerman is a global HR leader with over 30 years of senior director experience in the UK and internationally. He has spearheaded numerous high-profile projects at prestigious organisations, including the BBC, BP Plc, C&W, and the MOD Navy. Following a four-year tenure as Chief Human Resources Officer for a leading Middle Eastern tech company, John’s most recent role was at Fujitsu, where he successfully led the UK&I business through a major transition programme and managed Employee Relations across Europe. John is a Fellow of the Chartered Institute of Personnel Development (FCIPD) and a Leadership Fellow of St George’s House, Windsor Castle. He holds a master’s degree in business administration (MBA) and is a qualified Executive Coach with Henley Management College."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
